CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784558905
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway to introduce
OL,4,Ctemporary timetable after issues with
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FEast Midlands Railway has announced a
OL,8,Ftemporary reduced timetable from
OL,9,FMonday July 20 after performance and
OL,10,Freliability issues with their multi-
OL,11,Fmillion pound aurora fleet of trains.
OL,13,FThe railway operator, ran by Transport
OL,14,FUK says the reduced timetable will
OL,15,Fremain in place while the company
OL,16,Fworks with the manufacturer Hitachi
OL,17,FRail to resolve disruption for
OL,18,Fcustomers as soon as possible.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784558905
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway to introduce
OL,4,Ctemporary timetable after issues with
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FThey say the change is necessary after
OL,8,Fissues with the performance of Hitachi
OL,9,FRail's new class 810 fleet and the
OL,10,Fmaintenance of their existing class
OL,11,F222 fleet.
OL,13,FThe company say the new class 810
OL,14,Ffleet was designed to provide a
OL,15,Ftransition from the class 222 fleet,
OL,16,Fwith a period where both fleets would
OL,17,Foperate alongside one another.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784558905
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway to introduce
OL,4,Ctemporary timetable after issues with
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FThe aurora train is part of a 400
OL,8,Fmillion investment which East Midlands
OL,9,FRailway said will 'revolutionise rail
OL,10,Ftravel across the midland mainline and
OL,11,F'mark the beginning of a new era for
OL,12,Fthem'.
OL,14,FThe 33 trains feature improved
OL,15,Fseating, air conditioning and better
OL,16,Finformation screens, as well as
OL,17,Fadditional seats compared to the
OL,18,Fprevious fleet and more leg room.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784558905
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway to introduce
OL,4,Ctemporary timetable after issues with
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FA three-year delay in the first Class
OL,8,F810 trains coming into service,
OL,9,Ftogether with ongoing service
OL,10,Freliability and maintenance issues
OL,11,Facross both fleets, has significantly
OL,12,Fimpacted upon EMR's ability to run a
OL,13,Freliable Intercity service.
OL,15,FEast Midlands Railway say the class
OL,16,F810 fleet will now continue in a
OL,17,Fcontrolled manner throughout 2026 and
OL,18,F2027.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784558905
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway to introduce
OL,4,Ctemporary timetable after issues with
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FThe Class 810 fleet meets all required
OL,8,Fsafety standards and entered service
OL,9,Ffollowing the necessary testing and
OL,10,Fregulatory approvals. The railway
OL,11,Fprovider say that the trains have
OL,12,Fhowever not yet met the standard that
OL,13,Fthe operator experts.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784558905
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway to introduce
OL,4,Ctemporary timetable after issues with
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FWill Rogers, Managing Director at East
OL,8,FMidlands Railway, said: "The
OL,9,Fperformance of the Class 810 fleet has
OL,10,Ffallen below the levels we and our
OL,11,Fcustomers expect, and it is necessary
OL,12,Fto introduce a temporary reduced
OL,13,Ftimetable while we work with the
OL,14,Fmanufacturer, Hitachi Rail, to improve
OL,15,Fconsistency in service.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784558905
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway to introduce
OL,4,Ctemporary timetable after issues with
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,F"We recognise that this will be
OL,8,Fdisappointing for customers, and we
OL,9,Funderstand the frustration caused when
OL,10,Four Intercity services do not
OL,11,Fconsistently meet the standards they
OL,12,Frightly expect, which in turn puts our
OL,13,Ffrontline staff in an unenviable
OL,14,Fposition of trying to deliver
OL,15,Fexcellent customer service amidst
OL,16,Fongoing reliability challenges.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784558905
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway to introduce
OL,4,Ctemporary timetable after issues with
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,F"We are sorry for the significant
OL,8,Fdisruption and inconvenience these
OL,9,Fissues have caused our customers, and
OL,10,Fwe are committed to restoring the
OL,11,Freliable service they rightly expect."
OL,13,FITV Central has contacted Hitachi Rail
OL,14,Ffor comment.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
