OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784558905
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway to introduce
OL,4,Ctemporary timetable after issues with
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FCustomers who have already booked a
OL,8,Fticket and now find their service
OL,9,Fisn't running will be able to travel
OL,10,Fup to either two trains prior or two
OL,11,Ftrains after the affected service.
OL,12,FCustomers who decide not to travel can
OL,13,Frequest a full refund.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
